summary: This is Tanya, a Ningheim. I just made this for myself and a friend said it looked good so I decided to upload it. You are welcome to change it as you wish but please do not re-upload it as I spent a lot of time on her.
descriptionHtml:
[size=6]This mod requires the Ningheim Race Mod, Apachii Sky Hair Female Version, SKSE and Racemenu. It will not work without them. A follower version is coming soon.

To install place the file skyrim\data\skse\plugins\CharGen\Presets.

To use the preset you must first select the Ningheim Race and then the female setting. Then you must click the Preset tab then Load Preset then click Tanya.jslot.

[/size][size=4]The Ningheim Race- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35474/?

Apachii Sky Hair, YOU MUST GET THE FEMALE PACK- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?

SKSE- http://skse.silverlock.org/

RaceMenu- [/size]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?[size=4]
